"{\"uid\": \"oann.com-newsroom-paris-olympics-michael-phelps-disappointed-in-mens-usa-swimming-performance\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"OAN StaffBlake Wolf3:21 PM - Wednesday, August 7, 2024 Aside from a few standout swimmers, Michael Phelps expressed his disappointment in the Men's USA swimming results at the Paris Olympic games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 3, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/One_America_News_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"OAN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/One_America_News_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/One_America_News_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 92, \"end\": 106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0489403528274365e-27, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}, {\"begin\": 149, \"end\": 161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Swimming\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USA swimming\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Swimming\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Swimming\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PM\", \"from\": 24, \"to\": 26}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 40, \"to\": 46}, {\"ngram\": \"a few standout swimmers\", \"from\": 66, \"to\": 89}, {\"ngram\": \"his disappointment\", \"from\": 116, \"to\": 134}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympic games\", \"from\": 172, \"to\": 195}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me as a whole, I was pretty disappointed to see the U.S. swimming results,\\\" Phelps said in an Interview withUSA Today.\", \"from\": 199, \"to\": 322, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 280, \"end\": 286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999568715348, \"rank\": 4.311680924439514e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a whole\", \"from\": 210, \"to\": 217}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S. swimming results\", \"from\": 252, \"to\": 277}, {\"ngram\": \"an Interview withUSA\", \"from\": 295, \"to\": 315}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously, there were a few standout swims, and those you have to recognize.\\\"\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 401, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few standout swims\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 366}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Phelps did praise swimmer Bobby Finke for his \\\"unbelievable\\\" performance in the 1500-meter freestyle swim, which resulted in a gold medal as well as a new world record.\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 580, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 412, \"end\": 418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999568715348, \"rank\": 4.311680924439514e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}, {\"begin\": 438, \"end\": 449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Finke\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bobby Finke\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Finke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Finke\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his \\\"unbelievable\\\" performance\", \"from\": 454, \"to\": 484}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1500-meter freestyle swim\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 517}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 549}, {\"ngram\": \"a new world record\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have chills right now talking about it,\\\" Phelps said, regarding Finke.\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 655, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 626, \"end\": 632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999568715348, \"rank\": 4.311680924439514e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"chills\", \"from\": 590, \"to\": 596}, {\"ngram\": \"Finke\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 654}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That was one of the greatest swims in the Olympics, in my opinion.\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 723, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the greatest swims\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 691}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 707}, {\"ngram\": \"my opinion\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Being able to break that world record in the [manner] that he did it.\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 793, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that world record\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 761}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just taking it out, challenging the other guys just to make a move, he was prepared.\\\"\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 879, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the other guys\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 840}, {\"ngram\": \"a move\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 860}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the interview, Phelps also explained his concern for the future of the USA swimming team.\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 973, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 899, \"end\": 905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999568715348, \"rank\": 4.311680924439514e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}, {\"begin\": 955, \"end\": 967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Swimming\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USA swimming\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Swimming\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Swimming\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the interview\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 897}, {\"ngram\": \"his concern\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 932}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 947}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"One of the things that I have always said over the last couple of years is the rest of the world is catching up,\\\" Phelps said.\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 1104, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1092, \"end\": 1098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999568715348, \"rank\": 4.311680924439514e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the things\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 995}, {\"ngram\": \"the last couple\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1040}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1049}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1061}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1074}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think a lot of the things that we have done as a country for so long, the other people are catching up.\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1211, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1119}, {\"ngram\": \"the things\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1133}, {\"ngram\": \"a country\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1164}, {\"ngram\": \"the other people\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are doing the same thing.\\\"\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1243, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same thing\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 23x gold medal swimmer then issued an open challenge for American swimmers looking to obtain the same level of greatness as Phelps has achieved.\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1306, \"end\": 1314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999340998620937, \"rank\": 4.966580370070895e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1373, \"end\": 1379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999568715348, \"rank\": 4.311680924439514e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 23x gold medal swimmer\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1271}, {\"ngram\": \"an open challenge\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1301}, {\"ngram\": \"the same level\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1356}, {\"ngram\": \"greatness\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1369}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone thought what I was trying to do was impossible, and if somebody's trying to do it now, you guys will all say it's impossible,\\\" Phelps continued.\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1549, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1532, \"end\": 1538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999568715348, \"rank\": 4.311680924439514e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1404}, {\"ngram\": \"somebody\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1468}, {\"ngram\": \"you guys\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1500}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If somebody wants to do it and they want it bad enough, and they are willing to take the little baby steps that it takes to get there, then I want to see it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1709, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"somebody\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1562}, {\"ngram\": \"the little baby steps\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1657}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Phelps concluded the interview by saying, \\\"Records are made to be broken.\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1784, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1711, \"end\": 1717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999568715348, \"rank\": 4.311680924439514e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the interview\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1741}, {\"ngram\": \"Records\", \"from\": 1754, \"to\": 1761}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The records that I was chasing throughout my career motivated me.\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1850, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The records\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1796}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1836}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So hopefully I can motivate somebody to do the same thing.\\\"\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1910, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"somebody\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1887}, {\"ngram\": \"the same thing\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1908}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay informed!\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 1926, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Receive breaking news blasts directly to your inbox for free.\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1988, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"breaking news blasts\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1955}, {\"ngram\": \"your inbox\", \"from\": 1